    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "0030 1987\nABOVE SAN FRANCISCO\nSan Francisco International Airport has three separate terminals connected\nwith a central parking structure which can accommodate up to 7,000 cars at\none time. S.F.O. serves over 24 million passengers on over 380,000 flights\nannually and is only a 15-minute drive from downtown San Francisco.\nASF 36\nTHE CAMERON COLLECTION\n543 Howard Street • San Francisco, CA 94105\n2015,166\n2292."
